Aeropostale October same-store sales rise 3 pct
Thu Nov 8, 2007 9:29am EST

NEW YORK, Nov 8 (Reuters) - Teen clothing retailer Aeropostale Inc (ARO.N) said
on Thursday its sales at stores open at least a year rose 3 percent in October.

Analysts, on average, were expecting it to post a rise of 1.3 percent,
according to Reuters Estimates.

